    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345930/extras/87a8dec0be30cee171114261def98256.poster.avif?t=1717408914\" width=308 height=77 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345930/extras/87a8dec0be30cee171114261def98256.webm?t=1717408914\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><strong>HELL OF VERDUN</strong> is a first person horror game in which you'll experience the horrors of the First World War. <br>Will you manage to discover all the secrets and escape from this hell? It's up to you, soldier.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345930/extras/074f3f051038181a879a83ab47474e1a.webp?t=1717408914\" width=124 height=34 /></span><br>In <strong>HELL OF VERDUN</strong> is set in World War I in 1916, thousands of soldiers had already fallen.<br>As a German soldier, Hanz Meier, you are there. Your troops should attack the French fort near Verdun.<br>But everything will be different, the attack will not take place, but a whole new hell will arise.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345930/extras/a4846152221636e12b1cb1d4d8abdebd.webp?t=1717408914\" width=214 height=34 /></span><br>In <strong>HELL OF VERDUN</strong>, explore the trenches surrounding the Battle of Verdun.<br>Explore the horrors of the First World War and uncover its dark secrets<br>Terrible War.<br><br><strong>INVESTIGATION</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2345930/extras/b9d231b039d3b12913b153502729fa37.poster.avif?t=1717408914\" width=616 height=344 ><source src=\"http